# Ports and URLs are derived from .env.ports at the repo root.
# WEB_PORT, API_PORT are read from environment (set by with-ports.sh or .env.ports).
# VITE_API_URL and VITE_AUTH_URL are computed from API_PORT if not set.
#
# To override explicitly:
# PORT=4000
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8080
# VITE_AUTH_URL=http://localhost:8080
